.container
  You love
  .love-name
    = @calculate["fname"]
  and your love percentage is
  .love-percentage
    = @calculate["percentage"]
  %br
  The Love Calculator has determined:
  .love-result
    = @calculate["result"]
  %br
  .sentiment
    - if @calculate["percentage"].to_i >= 50
      Congratulations! Here is your message for your love:
      = raw @sentiment
    - else
      Sorry, you are not a match. Better luck next time!

      %br
      = link_to 'Try again?', root_path
